{"tid":1242570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普形容香港街頭示威者產生巨大影響","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:45:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"837143a4f8594b25cae92d668c8f1fc5bc290594","tid":1242570,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普形容，香港的街頭示威者與北京打交道時「十分有效」，明顯產生巨大影響，但他拒絕表明支持香港示威者對北京政府的特別訴求。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普接受《時代雜誌》專訪，被問到是否支持香港示威者的訴求，他回應說，應該由示威者為他們自己發聲，他同中國有自己的爭論，相信會成功解決，他會讓中國和香港的示威者自己解決問題，似乎問題亦可以解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463778-20190619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463778-20190619.htm&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b953ba35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463778-20190619.htm&h=3a386dbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463778-20190619.htm</a>"},{"pid":"30ff3a4a87cade8284f97d699773d2ce48405d0c","tid":1242570,"uid":250254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:08:17.000Z","msg":"巨大力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中銀有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要錢定要香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中銀短期拆息高滙豐40點子 「同連登仔呼籲搬存款有關」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242248</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你要錢定要香港!???<br />\n入黎睇下, 認同就幫手推post!!!"},{"pid":"a1f3483934c4f0b02273e38c517fff103f5a5dfe","tid":1242570,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:34:27.000Z","msg":"有紀錄片講過trump 係有仇必報既人<br />\n佢憎hk 憎到仆街😂"},{"pid":"7f61c7c3c9b5572d988164c5fb40a9cba3970bc6","tid":1242570,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f34